Minimum required packages

At least:

galera-4-26.4.25-1.el8.x86_64.rpm
boost-program-options-1.66.x86_64.rpm

But in practice, also grab:

boost-system
boost-thread
possibly socat (recommended for Galera environments)

On a machine with internet (same OS version - RHEL 8 / compatible):

mkdir garbd_rpms
cd garbd_rpms

dnf download --resolve galera-4-26.4.25-1.el8

This will download:

galera
boost-program-options
all dependencies automatically

Then copy the whole folder to your offline server.


On offline server:
cd garbd_rpms
sudo dnf install *.rpm

This avoids dependency issues completely.

galera-4 RPM contains garbd binary
After install, you should get:
/usr/sbin/garbd


Check:

which garbd
